title: It feels good to be home! Res Lease in Austin. 4 Beds, 2 Baths
posting_body: Check out this beautiful 2-stories home with four bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms in Travis county, Austin, TX!!
It is a beautiful town with friendly neighborhoods, plenty of shopping and dining options, excellent schools, and many recreational opportunities.
Everything this home offers is for you to enjoy, from its elegant wood floorings to the neutral colors and ample windows that bring in lots of sunlight, making it warm and inviting.
The well-designed kitchen will make anyone that loves to cook happy with its plentiful wood cabinetry, large pantry, and stainless steel appliances.

The amount of space this home provides with its bedrooms and flex areas will give the renters so much room to spread out and make it home and the opportunity to transform one room into a home office space.
There's also a fantastic privately fenced backyard waiting for your friends and family on the weekends or after a long day at work to have a relaxing moment.
Schedule your tour and apply for this home today!
